[[!meta title="Translate Tails using Weblate"]]

Most of Tails can be translated directly online, through a simple web interface,
after logging in with [Hosted Weblate](https://hosted.weblate.org/).

- [Most Tails translatable strings](https://hosted.weblate.org/projects/tor/tails-gui/)

Beware, we don't host Hosted Weblate, they do have their own privacy policy.

If you want to go further and [[translate the Tails website|translate]], please get in touch via our
translation mailing list.
